Debugging is the process of finding the root cause of a specific issue

30-40% of time goest to Debugging

It's helpfu with detailed logs

for example ssh with verbosity

Terraform has detailed logs that you can enable by setting the TF_LOG

You can set TF_LOG to one of the log levels (in order of decreasing verbosity)

Log Level :
TRACE DEBUG INFO WARN ERROR

To storing the logs to File

TF_LOG_PATH

to set env 
in Windows

in cmd    set TF_LOG=INFO
          set TF_LOG_PATH=terraform.log

in LInox/MacOs
in shell  export TF_LOG=INFO
          export TF_LOG_PATH=terraform.log